## Validation Checklist

Use this checklist to verify that your ported component meets all Aucctus requirements:

- [ ] **Imports**
  - [ ] All external component libraries removed (shadcn/ui, lucide-react, sonner, etc.)
  - [ ] All internal component imports added (@components)
  - [ ] No unused imports remain

- [ ] **Component Structure**
  - [ ] External component structure transformed to internal patterns
  - [ ] Card patterns replaced with appropriate div+SectionHeader structure
  - [ ] Child components properly extracted and composed

- [ ] **Styling**
  - [ ] All Tailwind utility classes replaced with Aucctus theme classes
  - [ ] All button styles use btn classes
  - [ ] All text styles use aucctus-text-* classes
  - [ ] All background styles use aucctus-bg-* classes
  - [ ] All border styles use aucctus-border-* classes
  - [ ] All hover styles use *-hover classes (not hover: prefix)
  - [ ] All icon components use proper stroke classes

- [ ] **Icons**
  - [ ] All lucide icons replaced with Icon component
  - [ ] All icons have variant prop
  - [ ] All icons have proper aucctus-stroke-* classes
  - [ ] All icons have explicit height and width

- [ ] **State Management**
  - [ ] Mock data implementation for state
  - [ ] ID-based CRUD operations (not index-based)
  - [ ] Proper immutable state updates
  - [ ] useMemo for derived state calculations
  - [ ] useCallback for handler functions
  - [ ] React.memo for component optimization where appropriate

- [ ] **Accessibility**
  - [ ] Semantic HTML maintained
  - [ ] ARIA attributes added where needed
  - [ ] Keyboard navigation supported
  - [ ] Color contrast requirements met

- [ ] **Performance**
  - [ ] No unnecessary re-renders
  - [ ] Proper dependency arrays in hooks
  - [ ] List virtualization for long lists
  - [ ] Proper loading states

- [ ] **Edge Cases**
  - [ ] Form validation handled properly
  - [ ] Complex UI interactions preserved
  - [ ] Error states handled

